            <div type="a">
                <column>6</column>
                <head>Plea for Old Maids</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"The very fact of being an old maid is prima facie evidence of the
                    possession of purity, prudence and self-denial; and these are essential to the
                    character of a perfect wife; without them no woman is worth having."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Defends women who have not married, commonly called "old maids." The
                    article argues that such women have the character traits of the perfect wife.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look>**</look>
            </div>
